        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "min by (probe) (eodc_e2e_probe_success{env=\"$env\", collection=~\"$collection\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{probe}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "description": "One row per probe type. Red = any selected collection failing that probe.\n\n\u2022 **root** \u2014 GET / \u2014 checks the STAC root endpoint responds with valid JSON\n\u2022 **collections_list** \u2014 GET /collections \u2014 checks the API lists collections\n\u2022 **collection_detail** \u2014 GET /collections/{id} \u2014 checks a specific collection loads\n\u2022 **items_list** \u2014 GET /collections/{id}/items \u2014 checks the items endpoint returns features\n\u2022 **search_post** \u2014 POST /search \u2014 checks the search index works and returns results\n\u2022 **asset_fetch** \u2014 HEAD on asset URL \u2014 checks data.eodc.eu asset URLs are reachable"
    },
